_header: The high astripotent auctor of all
_description: Lines for a mumming, spoken by Law — seven stanzas rhyme royal

BLHar2251.First Lines:
The high Astrapotent auctor of allVnder whos clayme conciste the
                    clymates…
BLHar2251.Last Lines:
…What by spirytuel and temporal laweAll transgressours bene
                    holdyn vnder Awe

Robbins,  Rossell Hope,
